headline: Palantir and Rio Tinto Renew Enterprise Contract and Extend Access to Palantir’s AI Platform
summary: DENVER, November 13, 2024--Palantir Technologies Inc. (NYSE:PLTR) has renewed its multi-year enterprise agreement with the Rio Tinto Group, one of the world’s leading mining and metals groups (ASX:RIO). The agreement extends the enterprise agreement for an additional 4 years and secures Rio Tinto’s ongoing access to the Palantir Artificial intelligence Platform ("AIP").
